Use any convenient make utility with the provided makefile (adaptions may be necessary).

Compilation options:

EC_ARCH_AMIGA_DICE  -  Set this when compiling under DCC on Amiga.
EC_ARCH_LINUX       -  Set this when compiling under Linux (Unix).
EC_ARCH_OSX         -  Set this when compiling under MacOS

EC_USE_GNU_READLINE -  Set this for to use GNU libreadline. This will
                       enable command history, full command line editing,
                       command history, and more.
EC_USE_EDITLINE     -  Set this to use libeditline.
